{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he paid off someone, and they dig a big hole, because my aunt was quite a heavy person.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They dig a big hole, I don't know, probably other people got out maybe through this there too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They got them out, and their apartment the Germans took over, because they lived in very elegant apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the whole building was taken by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were able to get them out that time, for that time being, but even short time was that time important.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every moment we could, we always hoped there would be-- soon the war would be over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who ever thought of this kind of destruction?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they go out, and-- and that's how we got together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For a while they lived with us, for a short time, until they found a bigger place to live.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another apartment, apartment-- a room somewhere, to-- for temporary life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was just-- everything, every moment, was just-- everything was temporary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But everybody was hoping that tomorrow would be end of war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody thought that it would be complete, this kind of annihilation of our culture, and life, and-- and freedom, and-- and everything what was considered life, that would be wiped off, wiped out in no time.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that time, he went home, and they got back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, I-- they put me and my sister, both of us, they had a shop, but they had a-- like a-- from the Jewish community, obviously, they got like a seal, that is taken over.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's nothing there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they put, to camouflage, they put it outside, that seal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had the entrance somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had the key to be able to go in the shop, in the back of the shop.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
